{"tid":2138241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張曉明抵港　據了解聽取處理立法會真空期意見","createTime":"2020-08-03T12:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T12:46:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d969120d584c2b0f3bb29c560a8b9eebbabcbaeb","tid":2138241,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:38:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541595-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541595-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=f17ac2ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541595-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e63db2d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541595-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港澳辦副主任張曉明抵港，會見部分建制派人士。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，他主要是聽取對押後立法會選舉，及如何處理立法會未來一年真空期的意見。有會面者提出宜讓所有現屆議員留任，但亦有人認為這樣做不合理，建議應讓選舉主任完成所有提名審核，凡提名無效的現任議員，都不應參與未來一年議會工作。<br />\n<br />\n有民主派議員說，不相信有「溫和」方案，會視乎議會是否仍有空間爭取「五大訴求」，再決定是否留任。"},{"pid":"4a959f5cc6a5f8b0dcdd3ff9b28f1214fba162b1","tid":2138241,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭話用緊急法推遲一年立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n乜公布之前, 唔係同中央溝通好架咩?<br />\n<br />\n依家公布咗, 行駛咗權力, 先至聽意見?<br />\n<br />\n做之前, 有無諗清楚?<br />\n<br />\n係唔係自製憲制危機?<br />\n<br />\n自製危機比中央?"},{"pid":"0b842a36838470dae93e69618158e0a155f702da","tid":2138241,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKf4OKt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKf4OKt.gif&h=e17d00b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36ef68533cc9fae7a046a2746c1f1611233639ac","tid":2138241,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://